      <para id="import-auto-idm816290992">A: We should remove the guard.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm780576864">B: That's a bad idea.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm910357376">A: Yes, you're right.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm215653696">B: Maybe we should use another machine.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm1043665408">A: That's a good idea.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm877512384">B: We could use a band saw.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm206089216">A: Yes, that's not a bad idea.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm1043689168">B: It would be safer.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm200684960">A: That's true and quicker.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm198437856">B: Exactly. </para>
