    <section id="import-auto-idm221146896">
      <title>End of section review  </title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm811151888">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm800173872">1) This socket is very dangerous. You…………………………get electrocuted.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm821939904">A)  should  B)  could  C)  must  D) have to</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm791743696">2) Loud noise can…………………………your hearing.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm242061616">A) help B) save  C) find  D) damage</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm197745856">3) You…………………………wear safety glasses.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm822999824">A) must  B)  need  C) have D) haven't</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm813682688">4) You…………………………remove guards from machinery</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm804609712">A) have B) mustn't C) must to D) know</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm204241952">5) Safety glasses protect your………………………</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm846259056">A) eyes B) nose C) ears D) feet</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm845406336">6) Steel toed boots protect your………………………</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm844487280">A) head B) eyes C) ears D) feet</para>
